HEADWORD: Climate
<hw>Cli"mate</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To dwell.</def>
<mark>[Poetic]</mark> <au>Shak.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Climatic</ent>⟦br⟧
